name: Ernest Nygard
review: God led me here, my loving family!!! My wife had a massive cluster of strokes a year after we started attending, they rallied around us, helping at home, with food, all kinds of gifts of love - we knew we'd come home!!!

name: Andrew Adcock
review: Wonderful people, great preaching. Very welcoming. Highly recommend.

name: Calvin Lang
review: Good biblical teaching, friendly people, and great Sunday school.
